high_descs: Face the round table on your left.
Pick up the spoon near the window.
Turn the opposite direction, then go to the sink to your right.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Go to the counter behind you.
Put the spoon in the second drawer from the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon away in a kitchen drawer.

high_descs: Turn to your left facing the round table
Turn left then head to the sink
Put the ladle in the sink and rinse it
Turn left then then cross the room face the cabinet counter
Open the second cabinet drawer then put in the  ladle then close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put the clean ladle in the cabinet drawer

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the round white table
Pick up the large spoon with a black handle from the table
Turn around and walk forward then turn right and approach the sink
Wash the spoon under water in the sink then remove it
Turn around and walk across to the kitchen counter
Open the top drawer second from left and put the spoon in it
anns.task_desc: Put the washed spoon in the kitchen drawer
